Youtify – The best free music search engine for Spotify Premium and YouTube
Youtify – The best music search engine for Spotify Premium and YouTube
With Youtify you can find all the music you want. You can search by Playlists, Songs, Albums or Artists, and enjoy all the music through Spotify or Youtube.
Now you can enjoy your Lists on any device - iPhone, iPad, Mac or PC - because you'll always have them available via your YouTube account username, whenever you want.
Youtify is the best app in the AppStore to discover and find music, since it has its own state-of-the-art search engine which uses the best Artists databases in Internet. Youtify is fast and very easy to use. It was developed by the best specialists in interface design and programming, with many years of experience, so that you may listen to your favourite artists in less than 5 seconds.
Try and download Youtify right now, you will not regret it!
Main features:
- Search by Playlist, Song, Album or Artist. - Enjoy the best music on Spotify or the best videos from your favourite artists on YouTube - We show you the most popular songs so that your searches become better and faster - If you have an AppleTV, you will be able to enjoy all your favourite videos on your TV thanks to the AirPlay technology. - If you have a Chromecast, you can also enjoy your music on television. - Set up the viewing of your videos in SD or HD quality. - Set up the Search so that it runs searches on Spotify or Youtube - Set up the Search so that it runs searches without age or country restrictions (moderated search)
This app is perfect for Spotify Premium users through the Spotify app, however, if you do not have the premium version, you can use it through YouTube.
This app complies with current legislation, and uses YouTube and Spotify public APIs.
Disclaimer: This is not an official product. This application has been created and it is the responsibility of KissApp. This application is not endorsed by or affiliated with Spotify and YouTube. Their names, brands and other issues of this application are trademarks and property of their respective owners.
